435
00:28:55,979 --> 00:28:56,659
It's fine.

436
00:28:56,659 --> 00:28:57,576
Come on, give it to me.

437
00:28:57,739 --> 00:28:58,696
Give it to me.

438
00:29:02,338 --> 00:29:03,298
