and help each other out in the future.

524
00:34:28,178 --> 00:34:29,499
Hello, I'm Mingshi.

525
00:34:29,640 --> 00:34:30,538
I'm Ye.

526
00:34:30,538 --> 00:34:31,432
I'm Chen.

527
00:34:31,738 --> 00:34:33,419
